    "Overall, the joint analysis of the results supports that, for JPEG Pleno, assigning either a balanced bitrate between or a larger portion color models lower more quality at high bitrates.",
    "provides but Bouquet, Thaidancer, and House_without_roof at mid-range bitrates R2 and R3, but is outperformed at R1 for StMichael, Soldier and Boxer.",
    "In general, the joint results allow for the existence of rate allocations better than the CTC without a clear indication of how this allocation should be defined.",
    "However, for V-PCC, P1 is usually the best strategy whenever a significant difference is observed.",
    "For the alternative strategies, direct comparisons generally attribute an advantage to P3, although significant differences are observed only for Bouquet and Soldier."
